FROM

WHERE

    AND SER_USER_ID = '*ROLE'
    AND SER_RUN = 'Y'

WITH component as (
SELECT
  JDEO_APPS_ID,
  JDEO_OBJECT,
  CPT_ID,
  CPT_COMPONENT
FROM
    JDE_OBJECTS
INNER JOIN
    SETTINGS_JDE_SY
    ON JDEO_SY = SYC_ID
INNER JOIN 
    SETTINGS_LIC_COMPONENTS
    ON SYC_CPT_ID = CPT_ID
)
SELECT
    DISTINCT
    SER_APPS_ID,
    CPT_ID,
    SER_ROLE_ID,
    SER_OBJECT,
    SERL_FORM,
    SER_VERSION,
    SER_RUN,
    SER_ROLE_ACTION_ID,
    SER_ADD,
    SER_CHG,
    SER_DEL,
    MENU_ROOT,
    MENU_ID,
    MENU_LEVEL1,
    MENU_LEVEL2,
    MENU_LEVEL3,
    MENU_LEVEL4,
    MENU_LEVEL5,
    MENU_LEVEL6,
    MENU_LEVEL7,
    MENU_LEVEL8,
    MENU_LEVEL9,
    MENU_SEQ_UKID
FROM
    SECURITY_RIGHTS
INNER JOIN
    SECURITY_MENUS
    ON MENU_APPS_ID = SER_APPS_ID
    AND MENU_SEQ_UKID = SER_MENU_SEQUKID
LEFT JOIN
    component
    ON JDEO_APPS_ID = SER_APPS_ID
    AND JDEO_OBJECT = SER_OBJECT
WHERE
    TRIM(SER_OBJECT) IS NOT NULL
    AND SER_USER_ID = '*ROLE'
    AND SER_RUN = 'Y'

SELECT
    LUSR_APPS_ID,
    LUSR_USER_ID,
    LUSR_DT_TRANSACTION
FROM (
SELECT
    LUSR_APPS_ID,
    LUSR_USER_ID,
    TO_CHAR(MAX(LUSR_DT_TRANSACTION),'yyyy-MM-dd') LUSR_DT_TRANSACTION
FROM
    LICENSE_JDE_USERS
LEFT JOIN
    SECURITY_USERS
    ON USR_APPS_ID = LUSR_APPS_ID
    AND TRIM(LUSR_USER_ID) = USR_ID
WHERE
    LUSR_APPS_ID  = LUSR_APPS_ID
    AND USR_ID IS NULL
    AND LUSR_DT_TRANSACTION  >= CURRENT_DATE  - 90
GROUP BY
    LUSR_APPS_ID,
    LUSR_USER_ID
) USERS_NOT_DECLARED

SELECT
    APPS_ID,
    CPT_ID,
    COMPLIANCE,
    ROUND(PRC_PRICE) PRC_PRICE,
    ROUND(COMPLIANCE * PRC_PRICE) TOTAL_PRICE,
    ROUND(PRC_SUPPORT) PRC_SUPPORT,
    ROUND(COMPLIANCE * PRC_SUPPORT * 3) TOTAL_SUPPORT,
    ROUND(COMPLIANCE * PRC_PRICE + COMPLIANCE * PRC_SUPPORT * 3) TOTAL_COMPLIANCE
FROM
((
SELECT
    APPS_ID,
    CPT_ID,
    USERS_COUNT,
    ACTIVE_USERS_COUNT,
    COALESCE(QUANTITY,0) SUBSCRIBED,
    COALESCE(QUANTITY,0) - (CASE WHEN ACTIVE_USERS_COUNT = 0 THEN USERS_COUNT ELSE ACTIVE_USERS_COUNT END)  COMPLIANCE
FROM
(
(SELECT
    APPS_ID,
    CPT_ID,
    USERS_COUNT,
    ACTIVE_USERS_COUNT
FROM
    LICENSE_JDE_USAGE
) LINKED_USERS
LEFT JOIN 
(
SELECT 
    LCA_APPS_ID,
    LCC_CPT_ID,
    SUM(LCC_QUANTITY) QUANTITY
FROM
    LICENSE_CSI_COMPONENTS
INNER JOIN
    LICENSE_CSI_APPS
    ON LCA_CSI_ID = LCC_CSI_ID
GROUP BY
    LCA_APPS_ID,
    LCC_CPT_ID
) ALL_COMPONENTS
    ON LCC_CPT_ID = CPT_ID 
    AND LCA_APPS_ID  = APPS_ID
) 
) ALL_COMPLIANCE
INNER JOIN 
(
SELECT 
    PRC_CPT_ID,
    PRC_PRICE,
    PRC_SUPPORT
FROM
    SETTINGS_LIC_PRICING
) PRICING ON PRC_CPT_ID = CPT_ID
) 
WHERE COMPLIANCE < 0

WITH activeUsers as (
SELECT
        USR_APPS_ID,COUNT(DISTINCT USR_ID) JDE_ACTIVE_USERS
    FROM
        SECURITY_USERS
    INNER JOIN
        SECURITY_ASSIGNMENTS
        ON RLU_APPS_ID = USR_APPS_ID
        AND RLU_USER_ID = USR_ID
    WHERE
        USR_STATUS = '01'
    GROUP BY USR_APPS_ID
),
transactionUsers as (
SELECT
        USR_APPS_ID,COUNT(DISTINCT USR_ID) JDE_TRANSACTION_USERS
    FROM
        SECURITY_USERS
    INNER JOIN
        LICENSE_JDE_USERS
        ON LUSR_APPS_ID = USR_APPS_ID
        AND TRIM(LUSR_USER_ID) = USR_ID
    WHERE
         USR_STATUS = '01'
          AND LUSR_DT_TRANSACTION  >= SYSDATE  - 90
    GROUP BY
        USR_APPS_ID
),
noTransactionUsers as (
SELECT
        USR_APPS_ID,COUNT(DISTINCT USR_ID) JDE_NOTRANSACTION_USERS
    FROM
        SECURITY_USERS
    LEFT JOIN
        LICENSE_JDE_USERS
        ON LUSR_APPS_ID = USR_APPS_ID
        AND TRIM(LUSR_USER_ID) = USR_ID
    WHERE
          USR_STATUS = '01'
          AND LUSR_USER_ID IS NULL
    GROUP BY
        USR_APPS_ID
),
transactionNoUsers as (
SELECT
        LUSR_APPS_ID,COUNT(DISTINCT LUSR_USER_ID) JDE_TRANSACTION_NOUSERS
    FROM
        LICENSE_JDE_USERS
    LEFT JOIN
        SECURITY_USERS
        ON USR_APPS_ID = LUSR_APPS_ID
        AND TRIM(LUSR_USER_ID) = USR_ID
    WHERE
      USR_ID IS NULL
      AND LUSR_DT_TRANSACTION  >= SYSDATE  - 90
    GROUP BY
        LUSR_APPS_ID
)
SELECT
    APPS_ID,
    NVL(JDE_ACTIVE_USERS,0) JDE_ACTIVE_USERS,
    NVL(JDE_TRANSACTION_USERS,0) JDE_TRANSACTION_USERS,
    NVL(JDE_NOTRANSACTION_USERS,0) JDE_NOTRANSACTION_USERS,
    NVL(JDE_TRANSACTION_NOUSERS,0) JDE_TRANSACTION_NOUSERS
FROM
    SETTINGS_APPLICATIONS 
LEFT JOIN 
    activeUsers ON APPS_ID = activeUsers.USR_APPS_ID
LEFT JOIN 
    transactionUsers ON APPS_ID = transactionUsers.USR_APPS_ID
LEFT JOIN 
    noTransactionUsers ON APPS_ID = noTransactionUsers.USR_APPS_ID
LEFT JOIN 
    transactionNoUsers ON APPS_ID = transactionNoUsers.LUSR_APPS_ID
WHERE APPS_TYPE = 'JDE'

WITH component as (

FROM

GROUP BY

SELECT
  LDAPD_GROUP,
  APPS_NAME,
  LDAP_NAME,
  LDAPD_DEPARTEMENT,
  LDAP_DESCRIPTION,
  LDAP_EXPIRES,
  LDAP_COMPANY,
  LDAP_TITLE,
  USR_ID,
  USR_NAME,
  USR_REGISTRATION,
  USR_STATUS,
  USR_DT_LOGIN,
  USR_DT_CREATION,
  RLU_ROLE_ID FROM
(
  SELECT
    LDAPD_GROUP,
    C.APPS_NAME,
    LDAP_NAME,
    LDAPD_DEPARTEMENT,
    LDAP_DESCRIPTION,
    LDAP_EXPIRES,
    LDAP_COMPANY,
    LDAP_TITLE,
    A.USR_ID,
    A.USR_NAME,
    A.USR_REGISTRATION,
    A.USR_STATUS,
    A.USR_DT_LOGIN,
    A.USR_DT_CREATION,
    (
    SELECT 
      STRING_AGG(RLU_ROLE_ID, ',' ORDER BY RLU_ROLE_ID)      
    FROM (
      SELECT RLU_ROLE_ID FROM 
        SECURITY_ASSIGNMENTS
      WHERE 
        RLU_USER_ID = A.USR_ID AND RLU_APPS_ID = A.USR_APPS_ID ORDER BY RLU_ROLE_ID) ALL_ASSIGNMENTS
    ) RLU_ROLE_ID
  FROM
    SECURITY_LDAP_DPT
  INNER JOIN
    SECURITY_LDAP ON LDAP_DEPARTMENT = LDAPD_DEPARTEMENT
  INNER JOIN
    SETTINGS_APPLICATIONS LDAP  ON LDAP.APPS_ID = LDAP_APPS_ID
  LEFT JOIN 
    (SECURITY_USERS A INNER JOIN SETTINGS_APPLICATIONS C  ON A.USR_APPS_ID = C.APPS_ID) ON 
      UPPER(A.USR_REGISTRATION)  =  UPPER(LDAP_DESCRIPTION)  
      OR  UPPER(A.USR_ID)  =  UPPER(LDAP_ACCOUNT)
    WHERE A.USR_ID IS NOT NULL
  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    LDAPD_GROUP ,
    APPS_NAME ,
    LDAP_NAME ,
    LDAPD_DEPARTEMENT,
    LDAP_DESCRIPTION,
    LDAP_EXPIRES,
    LDAP_COMPANY,
    LDAP_TITLE, NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL , NULL
  FROM 
    SECURITY_LDAP_DPT
  INNER JOIN 
    SECURITY_LDAP ON LDAP_DEPARTMENT = LDAPD_DEPARTEMENT
  INNER JOIN 
    SETTINGS_APPLICATIONS ON APPS_ID = LDAP_APPS_ID
) ALL_ROLES

SELECT

  USERS_COUNT,
  RLU_ROLE_ID,
  USR_ID
FROM
  (
  SELECT
    APPS_ID,
    RLU_ROLE_ID,
    count(distinct USR_ID) USERS_COUNT,
    MAX(USR_ID) USR_ID
  FROM
    (
    SELECT
      APPS_ID,
      USR_ID,
      (
      SELECT
        STRING_AGG(RLU_ROLE_ID, ',' ORDER BY RLU_ROLE_ID)
      FROM
        (
        SELECT
          RLU_ROLE_ID
        FROM
          SECURITY_ASSIGNMENTS
        WHERE
          RLU_USER_ID = USR_ID
          AND RLU_APPS_ID = APPS_ID
        ) ALL_ROLES
      ) RLU_ROLE_ID
      FROM
        SECURITY_USERS
      INNER JOIN
        SETTINGS_APPLICATIONS
        ON APPS_ID = USR_APPS_ID
      WHERE
        USR_STATUS = '01'
    ) ROLES_DETAILS
  GROUP BY
    APPS_ID,
    RLU_ROLE_ID
  ) ROLES_MATRIX
WHERE
  TRIM(RLU_ROLE_ID) is not null

SELECT DISTINCT
    USR_APPS_ID,
    USR_ID,
    USR_NAME,
    CASE WHEN USR_STATUS = '01' THEN '01' ELSE 'N' END USR_STATUS,
    USRD_ULCTR,
    USRD_MCCO,
    USRD_MCMCU,
    USRD_MCRP08,
    USR_DT_CREATION,    
    CPT_COMPONENT,
    LAST_USAGE
FROM
    SECURITY_USERS_DATA
INNER JOIN
    SECURITY_USERS
    ON USR_ID = USRD_ID 
LEFT JOIN
    (SELECT 
        LOUT_APPS_ID, 
        CPT_COMPONENT,
        LOUT_USER, 
        MAX(LOUT_USAGE) LAST_USAGE 
    FROM
      LICENSE_JDE_OUT 
    INNER JOIN
      JDE_OBJECTS
      ON JDEO_APPS_ID = LOUT_APPS_ID
      AND JDEO_OBJECT = LOUT_OBJECT
    INNER JOIN
      SETTINGS_JDE_SY
      ON JDEO_SY = SYC_ID
    INNER JOIN 
      SETTINGS_LIC_COMPONENTS
      ON SYC_CPT_ID = CPT_ID
    GROUP BY
        LOUT_APPS_ID, 
        CPT_COMPONENT,
        LOUT_USER
    )
    ON LOUT_USER = USR_ID AND LOUT_APPS_ID = USR_APPS_ID

SELECT
    USR_APPS_ID,
    USR_ID,
    USRD_AN8,
    USR_STATUS,
    USR_DT_CREATION ,
    USR_DT_LOGIN ,
    USRP_PRIVILEGED,
    USRP_TECHNICAL,
    USRP_GENERIC,
    USRP_IS_LINKED,
    USRP_ID_LINKED
FROM
    (
    SELECT
        USR_APPS_ID,
        USR_ID,
        USRD_AN8,
        USR_REGISTRATION,
        USR_STATUS,
        USR_DT_CREATION,
        USR_DT_LOGIN,
        USRP_PRIVILEGED,
        USRP_TECHNICAL,
        USRP_GENERIC,
        USRP_IS_LINKED,
        USRP_ID_LINKED
    FROM
        SECURITY_USERS
    INNER JOIN
        SECURITY_USERS_DATA
        ON USRD_APPS_ID = USR_APPS_ID AND USRD_ID = USR_ID
    LEFT JOIN
        SECURITY_USERS_PROP
        ON USRP_APPS_ID = USR_APPS_ID AND USRP_ID = USR_ID
    WHERE
        (USRD_APPS_ID,USRD_AN8) IN
        ( SELECT
            USRD_APPS_ID,
            USRD_AN8
        FROM
            SECURITY_USERS_DATA
        GROUP BY
            USRD_APPS_ID,USRD_AN8
        HAVING
            COUNT(*)  > 1 )
        ) DUPLICATE_USERS

SELECT
  'Users / Roles' SERIES,
  CAST(USR_ID AS INTEGER) USR_ID,
  CAST(ROL_ID AS INTEGER) ROL_ID
FROM
(
SELECT
  (SELECT count(distinct USR_ID) CRT_COUNT FROM SECURITY_USERS) USR_ID,
  (SELECT count(distinct ROL_ID) CRT_COUNT FROM SECURITY_ROLES) ROL_ID
)

SELECT
    USR_APPS_ID,
    USR_ID,
    USR_NAME,
    USR_STATUS,
    USR_DT_CREATION,
    USR_DT_LOGIN,
    RLU_ROLE_ID
FROM
(
SELECT
    USR_APPS_ID,
    USR_ID,
    USR_NAME,
    USR_STATUS,
    USR_DT_CREATION,
    USR_DT_LOGIN,
    (
        SELECT
              STRING_AGG(RLU_ROLE_ID, ',' ORDER BY RLU_ROLE_ID) 
        FROM
          (
           SELECT
              RLU_ROLE_ID
           FROM
             SECURITY_ASSIGNMENTS
           WHERE
             RLU_USER_ID = USR_ID
              AND RLU_APPS_ID = USR_APPS_ID
           ) ALL_ASSIGNMENTS
    ) RLU_ROLE_ID
    FROM
        SECURITY_USERS
    WHERE
        USR_STATUS = '01'
) MATRIX_USERS
